Condor:

Condor unconcious in Beastbox's interrogatory, as soon as Megatron 
altered his memory banck, Condor started to fight against his 
memories and planted memories... 

Inside his mind he remembered all things that he had done, his 
commander and fellows... he wake up again in Starjumper, and fought 
again in CF against Decepticos... but memories planted made him 
doubt... He wasn't sure... Who was he? What was his faction?? 
Maximal? Decepticon?
